msgid "To set a new key binding, press Tab twice to put the cursor on Add, then press Enter. In the small dialog box brought up type the name of the custom key binding, like firefox, press Tab, type the name to the associated command, in this case firefox, then press Tab twice to put the cursor on Apply and press Enter."
